{"tid":529340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国直播平台有奬問題 將港、台並列加拿大為'國家'捱轟","createTime":"2018-01-14T17:10:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-15T01:18:17.000Z","uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f753faabf3c9b440961350b803823935207ce2b5","tid":529340,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T17:10:54.000Z","msg":"繼內地傳媒近日接連爆出萬豪酒店、達美航空等外資公司中文官網，將港澳台藏列為「國家」後，內地直播平台「花椒直播」亦出現類似問題。有網民發現，「花椒」旗下節目「百萬贏家」於周六（13日）直播期間，問及藝人王祖賢現時定居國家時，其選項出現「香港」、「台灣」和「加拿大」，事件曝光後旋即惹起爭議。<br />\n<br />\n「百萬赢家」是由「花椒」推出的益智類直播答題節目，參與直播的網民答對12題即可獲得獎金。<br />\n<br />\n據官方事後道歉聲明所示，平台將錯誤歸咎於「出題者不慎」所致，強調「香港和台灣都是中國領土不可分割的一部分」，並表示會「加強後續出題的審核環節和流程」，以避免再發生類似情況。<br />\n<br />\n（中新網/聯合新聞網）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180114/s00004/1515909230729\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180114%2Fs00004%2F1515909230729&d=z9rTh6gFYq%2BDeBJzwrH5aMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=cb46cd0f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180114%2Fs00004%2F1515909230729&h=2d112428\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180114/s00004/1515909230729</a>"},{"pid":"d4e0c9e2a8a7c2b4a96386330e67d92bc9c5d443","tid":529340,"uid":25635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T17:13:25.000Z","msg":"政治不正確，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e22ffd1a16ba293de3bf608e2107124c9172c59e","tid":529340,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T17:14:31.000Z","msg":"幾時都淘寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n班大陸紅衛兵咪撚扮盲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea81cdd2c9347018dc9c9643803d0e06d44adf2b","tid":529340,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e22ffd1a16ba293de3bf608e2107124c